title: Bitcoin Ordinals 'Quantum Cat' Sells for Over $250K at Sotheby's
description: The “Genesis Cat” Bitcoin art by FAR fetched 6.31 BTC at Sotheby's, with the wider Ordinals sale bringing in nearly $1.1 million in total.

title: Binance and SEC both criticized by judge during latest court hearing
description:
A Monday court hearing addressed the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC)’s ongoing charges against Binance, Reuters reported on Jan. 22. title: US Senator Marco Rubio Warns BRICS Expansion Threatens Western Sanctions’ Effectiveness
